snippet: The conglomerate called off the sale of ParknShop, which operates 345 stores in Hong Kong, China and Macau, in favor of expanding in China.
lead_paragraph: The conglomerate called off the sale of ParknShop, which operates 345 stores in Hong Kong, China and Macau, in favor of expanding in China.
